  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"viewencapsulation\">ViewEncapsulation</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label enum\">enum</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation</a> } from <a href=\"api/core\">'@angular/core'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts#L1-L36\">core/src/metadata/view.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"enum-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ivgu86loww6mg4fq1brezlnd\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nenum <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\">Emulated: 0</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Native\">Native: 1</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\">None: 2</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"Emulated\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">Emulated: 0</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cq3h1w7etidqga2avd90tmdv6\">通过在宿主元素上添加一个包含代理 ID 的属性，并预处理通过 \n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\">styles</a> 或 \n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\">styleUrls</a> 提供的样式规则，并将新的宿主元素属性添加到所有选择器，来模拟 \n<code>Native</code> 样式作用域。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dly6uuk3bwpezgco0668ume4u\">这是默认选项。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"Native\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">Native: 1</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8vq3injvhqsf61vhdlaocesj2\">使用渲染器的原生封装机制。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cd6iyy4cwtadwf4ikztfnavke\">对于 DOM，这意味着使用 \n<a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/\">Shadow DOM</a>，并为组件的宿主元素创建一个 ShadowRoot。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"None\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">None: 2</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bgxq23wx2l2qj0naa6dvjfmf2\">不提供任何模板或样式封装。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ID\n - api/core/CompilerOptions\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/RenderComponentType\n - api/core/RendererType2\n - guide/component-styles\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component#styleUrls\n - api/core/Component#styles\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Native\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#members\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#overview\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#viewencapsulation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts#L1-L36\n - https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
